                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                                    <p class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".2s" style="text-align: justify;">Every form of worship has its unique characteristics, rooted in the fundamental triad (‘Triputi’) of worshiper, worship, and the object of worship. However, this raises a profound question: how can one worship Brahman,
